<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About BouncieHouse</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick-theme.min.css">
  <style>
    .about-container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: 700;
      /* color: #007bff; */
    }
    .carousel {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 20px auto;
    }
    .carousel img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #007bff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
    .scrolling-text {
      font-size: 20px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1><span class="hightext-blue">Welcome to BouncieHouse Rentals</span></h1>
    
    <p class="scrolling-text">We're revolutionizing the way you experience bounce house rentals! Connect with bounce house operators effortlessly, book the perfect bounce house, select your date, and pay securely online. All in one simple, dynamic platform.</p>
    
    <p>BouncieHouse is not just a platform; it's a community where bounce house operators and customers come together for fun and memorable experiences. Operators can easily list their bounce houses, manage bookings, and watch their business grow. Customers get access to a wide range of bounce houses, all available at their fingertips.</p>
    
    <p>Our goal is to provide a seamless, enjoyable experience for both bounce house operators and their customers. We're dedicated to making your party planning as easy as a bounce!</p>

    <p>Join our community today and start bouncing into new opportunities!</p>
    
    <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-form btn-small">Sign Up Now</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
      $('.carousel').slick({
        dots: true,
        infinite: true,
        speed: 500,
        slidesToShow: 1,
        slidesToScroll: 1
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
